{"tid":1135271,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"誇張！ 支那阿伯下飛機不想等 擅自開啟逃生門","createTime":"2019-05-02T07:57:55.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-02T08:15:32.000Z","uid":32511,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"5f1e2c3e127ee1e22a8c983de2b0a8e7cd8a8a0f","tid":1135271,"uid":32511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:57:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_phpN8GEIU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_phpN8GEIU.jpg&h=c4678895&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n近日中國浙江一位阿伯因為心急，下飛機時竟然打開緊急逃生門，結果被警方逮捕，處以拘役10天。<br />\n<br />\n《星島日報》報導，這起事件發生在中國浙江舟山普陀山機場，當時一架從山東出發的山東航空客機抵達普陀山機場後，許多乘客等著下機，一名65歲宋姓阿伯卻因為自己坐的位置較後方，嫌排隊的人多，竟然突發奇想「下飛機還要等會兒，這裏不是有個門嗎？終是打開看看。」結果發現逃生門外沒有階梯，又回到機艙。<br />\n<br />\n報導指出，警方事後逮捕宋男，並表示未有航班遭到延誤等情事，宋男被處以10天的行政拘留。"},{"pid":"3c5f9b29a5a92c1ae919174b31ea338d4a69193d","tid":1135271,"uid":241810,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:58:38.000Z","msg":"Oops I did it again"},{"pid":"b92f1ea04d3be82c0dbb1635e313a4a20f077e0d","tid":1135271,"uid":43005,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T07:59:36.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">契弟走得摩呀！！！</span>"},{"pid":"6816f96ff0f8d3bd78b01f1f6f9075083504666b","tid":1135271,"uid":37661,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:00:41.000Z","msg":"好彩係雞翼<br />\n<br />\n如果係有埋充氣滑梯<br />\n<br />\n計埋條數俾佢就過癮<br />\n<br />\n乜阿豬阿狗都坐得緊急出口位嘅咩？"},{"pid":"235f5b548aaccb9f4476814a573ba3746e7289ce","tid":1135271,"uid":62247,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:02:22.000Z","msg":"佢點樣跳落地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好高喎"},{"pid":"aa13edfcc6c15429493ae3f9e8b8f89382cd8129","tid":1135271,"uid":193642,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-02T08:04:10.000Z","msg":"行政拘留真係好駛好用<img src=\"/assets/face